</div>

<ul id="home" selected="true">
    
  <% if System::get_property('platform') != 'WP7'%>    
    <li>UTF-8 encoded string: <br/><%= "Utf8 String".force_encoding( Encoding::UTF_8) %></li>
  <% end %>

    <li>Russian text(7 Letters): Евгений</li>
    <li>Greeting text from app\lang\lang_* : <br/><%= Localization::Views[:greeting] %></li>
    <li>Some Myth About Testing: <br/><%= Localization::Views[:abttest] %></li>
    <li>Time.now.to_formatted_s("%a, %d %b %Y %H:%M:%S %z"): <br/><%= Time.now.strftime("%a, %d %b %Y %H:%M:%S %z") %></li>
    <li>Time.now.to_formatted_s(:long): <br/><%= Time.now.to_formatted_s(:long) %></li>
    <li>Time.now.strftime("%B %d, %Y %H:%M"): <br/><%= Time.now.strftime("%B %d, %Y %H:%M") %></li>
    <li>Date.today.to_formatted_s(:long): <br/><%= Date.today.to_formatted_s(:long) %></li>
    <li>Date.today.strftime("%B %e, %Y"): <br/><%= Date.today.strftime("%B %e, %Y") %></li>
    <li>Rho::NumberHelper::number_to_currency(10000): <br/><%= Rho::NumberHelper.number_to_currency(10000) %></li>
</ul>

